WEBVTT

01:43.090 --> 01:46.090
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.110 --> 01:49.000
[Episode 13]

02:11.620 --> 02:12.900
Why are you sighing?

02:14.590 --> 02:15.110
What?

02:16.690 --> 02:18.050
You don't want your son to leave?

02:18.430 --> 02:19.780
Everything is fine,

02:20.070 --> 02:21.260
but he's suddenly moving out.

02:21.829 --> 02:22.240
What?

02:22.270 --> 02:23.180
He doesn't want to live with me?

02:23.800 --> 02:25.150
He thinks I meddle too much,

02:25.190 --> 02:25.710
doesn't he?

02:26.670 --> 02:28.020
Don't overthink.

02:29.070 --> 02:30.400
He's an adult now.

02:30.440 --> 02:31.400
Didn't he live by himself

02:31.430 --> 02:32.630
in Jinzhou?

02:32.790 --> 02:34.200
He's used to it.

02:36.710 --> 02:38.000
Judging from your tone,

02:38.710 --> 02:40.560
you know why he's moving,

02:40.950 --> 02:41.500
right?

02:43.750 --> 02:44.670
Tell me.

02:47.079 --> 02:49.270
Nothing really escapes

02:49.350 --> 02:51.040
Officer Jiang's sharp eyes.

02:51.070 --> 02:51.860
Of course.

02:51.950 --> 02:53.230
I'm an experienced criminal police officer.

02:55.380 --> 02:56.410
If I tell you,

02:56.670 --> 02:57.470
you can't tell our son

02:57.550 --> 02:58.510
I told you.

03:00.350 --> 03:01.150
Here's the thing.

03:02.070 --> 03:03.080
Dr. Lu has been

03:03.390 --> 03:04.950
in a little bit of trouble lately.

03:05.510 --> 03:06.770
So our son

03:07.310 --> 03:08.040
wants to move

03:08.060 --> 03:09.210
near her

03:09.240 --> 03:10.490
so they can take care of each other.

03:10.840 --> 03:11.720
That's good.

03:11.750 --> 03:12.270
Yeah.

03:12.270 --> 03:12.990
He should.

03:15.650 --> 03:16.400
They say,

03:16.510 --> 03:17.780
"A grown daughter's hard to keep."

03:18.200 --> 03:19.070
But look at my son.

03:19.110 --> 03:19.970
Now that he's in love,

03:19.990 --> 03:21.490
he just bolts off faster than a rabbit.

03:21.630 --> 03:22.680
Can't rely on him at all.

03:22.840 --> 03:24.030
Alright. I'll go wash the dishes.

03:25.160 --> 03:27.260
You're just saying that.

03:28.329 --> 03:29.420
You secretly love it!

04:05.270 --> 04:06.900
Going out so early?

04:07.440 --> 04:08.480
Is she going to work?

04:12.480 --> 04:12.960
Hey.

04:13.000 --> 04:13.770
Chengyi.

04:13.990 --> 04:15.940
I've sent you Deng Man's case files.

04:17.630 --> 04:18.140
Okay.

04:18.160 --> 04:18.850
Thank you, Director Xing.

04:20.470 --> 04:21.440
Yesterday, Sihan and I

04:21.470 --> 04:22.029
checked the surveillance footage.

04:22.070 --> 04:23.520
The murderer definitely scoped out

04:23.550 --> 04:24.670
the route beforehand.

04:24.790 --> 04:25.960
He found a blind spot,

04:26.000 --> 04:27.430
stuffed Wang Qianqian into the trunk,

04:27.470 --> 04:28.750
and then got right onto the ring road.

04:29.230 --> 04:30.420
The ring road?

04:31.350 --> 04:32.080
At that time,

04:32.110 --> 04:33.490
there must have been hundreds of cars passing by.

04:33.590 --> 04:34.270
It's impossible to find him.

04:34.310 --> 04:34.990
Exactly.

04:35.030 --> 04:36.400
Filtering all that data

04:36.430 --> 04:37.590
will take at least a month.

04:38.510 --> 04:39.300
How's it going on your side?

04:40.430 --> 04:41.460
Don't even mention it.

04:41.540 --> 04:42.740
To find the person

04:42.950 --> 04:44.190
pretending to be Deng Man,

04:44.430 --> 04:45.530
I went all the way to the suburbs,

04:45.680 --> 04:46.280
but since

04:46.310 --> 04:47.740
it was too long ago,

04:47.909 --> 04:48.480
the security footage was overwritten,

04:48.500 --> 04:49.340
and the trail went cold.

04:52.710 --> 04:53.390
Dr. Lu?

04:54.210 --> 04:55.050
Dr. Lu?

04:57.150 --> 04:58.040
Why are you here?

04:58.740 --> 04:59.400
I…

04:59.430 --> 05:00.500
Are you here for Captain Jiang?

05:01.360 --> 05:02.280
No, no.

05:02.840 --> 05:03.900
I came to see you.

05:04.130 --> 05:06.900
[Anshan, Ninghai Public Security
Criminal Investigation Unit]

05:06.070 --> 05:06.500
Okay.

05:12.640 --> 05:13.350
Thank you.

05:18.630 --> 05:19.190
Dr. Lu.

05:19.660 --> 05:21.020
What brought you here today?

05:24.400 --> 05:25.280
I found that

05:26.550 --> 05:27.680
Deng Man and Wang Qianqian

05:27.710 --> 05:28.850
were killed

05:29.060 --> 05:30.110
in the same place.

05:36.340 --> 05:37.180
This place.

05:37.430 --> 05:38.700
I know this place.

05:39.290 --> 05:41.760
[A Woman Drowned in the Chanson Artificial Lake]

05:43.590 --> 05:44.610
Thank you, Dr. Lu,

05:44.950 --> 05:45.810
for coming here

05:45.840 --> 05:46.890
to tell us about this.

05:47.310 --> 05:48.060
Dr. Lu.

05:48.409 --> 05:49.200
I'd like to know

05:49.230 --> 05:50.990
what your relationship

05:51.030 --> 05:52.080
with Deng Man was.

05:53.150 --> 05:54.340
She was

05:55.540 --> 05:56.680
my best friend.

05:59.590 --> 06:00.270
Well,

06:00.430 --> 06:01.320
something similar

06:01.350 --> 06:02.960
happened to two of your good friends.

06:03.110 --> 06:04.560
Do you think

06:04.630 --> 06:06.110
their deaths are related?

06:12.070 --> 06:12.750
I heard

06:12.800 --> 06:14.460
you've met Deng Man recently, right?

06:15.310 --> 06:15.850
Yes.

06:16.870 --> 06:17.510
I…

06:19.310 --> 06:20.450
I've met her twice.

06:21.070 --> 06:21.740
She wore

06:21.790 --> 06:23.150
the same clothes and hairpin

06:23.900 --> 06:25.330
as Deng Man.

06:26.540 --> 06:27.060
But

06:27.910 --> 06:29.060
she's not Deng Man.

06:29.700 --> 06:30.400
Yes.

06:31.070 --> 06:32.230
The case of Deng Man

06:32.270 --> 06:33.150
was closed eight years ago.

06:33.180 --> 06:34.960
So we don't know much

06:35.000 --> 06:35.880
about her case.

06:35.920 --> 06:37.170
Now that you're here,

06:37.350 --> 06:38.220
I want to know

06:38.270 --> 06:39.150
if Deng Man had

06:39.230 --> 06:40.390
any relatives and friends

06:40.510 --> 06:41.680
we can talk to.

06:42.630 --> 06:43.310
I don't think

06:43.350 --> 06:44.390
she had any relatives.

06:45.060 --> 06:46.270
In college…

06:48.870 --> 06:50.310
Tang Jie and I were her only friends.

06:50.670 --> 06:51.470
There was no one else.

06:53.070 --> 06:55.340
Did she have friends

06:55.470 --> 06:56.900
whom you don't know?

06:57.270 --> 06:58.300
Or people

06:58.550 --> 06:59.070
she met online.

07:03.190 --> 07:04.080
I don't know.

07:32.510 --> 07:34.570
Director Xing called me just now.

07:34.600 --> 07:35.470
He said you want to know

07:35.470 --> 07:36.470
about Deng Man's case.

07:36.909 --> 07:37.350
Yes.

07:37.380 --> 07:39.060
I've been investigating a case recently.

07:39.090 --> 07:40.830
I think it might be related

07:40.950 --> 07:41.960
to Deng Man's case.

07:42.310 --> 07:43.030
You handled

07:43.050 --> 07:44.420
Deng Man's case back then.

07:44.560 --> 07:45.780
So I want to talk to you.

07:46.350 --> 07:47.590
You know Deng Man?

07:47.810 --> 07:49.050
We went to the same college.

07:49.870 --> 07:50.460
Mr. Yang.

07:51.020 --> 07:52.370
Did Deng Man

07:52.710 --> 07:53.710
take her own life back then?

07:54.120 --> 07:56.159
Deng Man was drowned.

07:57.110 --> 07:57.800
When we

07:57.830 --> 07:59.520
found her body,

07:59.990 --> 08:02.470
there were no obvious injuries on her body.

08:03.790 --> 08:04.810
There was a suicide note

08:04.900 --> 08:06.270
beside her.

08:06.430 --> 08:08.670
The analysis of the handwriting

08:10.400 --> 08:11.330
confirmed that

08:12.120 --> 08:13.440
she wrote it.

08:14.430 --> 08:15.340
At that time,

08:15.430 --> 08:17.190
we conducted an investigation

08:17.900 --> 08:18.680
and found that

08:19.550 --> 08:20.510
before Deng Man died,

08:20.540 --> 08:22.280
she had big mood swings.

08:22.550 --> 08:23.310
So,

08:23.330 --> 08:25.030
we decided

08:25.950 --> 08:28.400
she committed suicide.

08:29.790 --> 08:30.780
Looking at it now,

08:31.030 --> 08:31.890
it was very simple.

08:32.350 --> 08:33.270
The evidence

08:33.650 --> 08:34.659
was interconnected,

08:34.990 --> 08:36.039
forming a perfect loop

08:37.309 --> 08:38.409
with no room for doubt.

08:43.470 --> 08:43.990
By the way,

08:44.910 --> 08:46.530
five years after Deng Man's death,

08:46.630 --> 08:47.350
we

08:47.390 --> 08:49.330
received an anonymous letter.

08:50.170 --> 08:51.360
According to this letter,

08:51.920 --> 08:53.790
Deng Man didn't commit suicide.

08:54.950 --> 08:57.130
The writer asked us to reinvestigate

08:57.190 --> 08:58.130
the cause of her death.

09:00.590 --> 09:01.610
Mr. Yang,

09:01.710 --> 09:03.810
the source of that anonymous letter...

09:03.950 --> 09:05.870
That anonymous letter was printed.

09:06.080 --> 09:07.560
We checked

09:07.590 --> 09:08.350
the sender's information.

09:08.430 --> 09:09.550
It was all fake.

09:09.990 --> 09:11.750
We did some further investigation,

09:11.870 --> 09:13.790
but we didn't find any new clues.

09:14.190 --> 09:14.870
Therefore,

09:15.350 --> 09:17.560
the conclusion remains suicide.

09:17.950 --> 09:20.410
Did this letter mention

09:21.020 --> 09:22.340
why Deng Man

09:22.430 --> 09:23.680
didn't commit suicide?

09:23.790 --> 09:25.290
Did it offer any clues or evidence?

09:25.470 --> 09:27.740
There was just this letter.

09:28.020 --> 09:29.340
Nothing else.

09:29.600 --> 09:30.840
So we thought

09:31.380 --> 09:32.490
it might be

09:32.710 --> 09:33.440
from a friend of Deng Man

09:33.470 --> 09:35.240
who wouldn't accept her suicide.

09:41.030 --> 09:41.750
Mr. Yang.

09:41.830 --> 09:44.070
Did Deng Man mention

09:44.110 --> 09:45.080
why she took her own life

09:45.110 --> 09:46.380
on the suicide note?

09:46.750 --> 09:47.310
No.

09:49.110 --> 09:50.610
Besides,

09:51.150 --> 09:52.740
her suicide note

09:52.830 --> 09:54.470
was written in a messy way

09:54.990 --> 09:57.280
with many incoherent sentences.

09:57.870 --> 09:59.600
We all thought

10:01.430 --> 10:02.320
it should have been

10:02.390 --> 10:03.910
a relationship problem.

10:06.470 --> 10:08.190
Then I retired,

10:08.830 --> 10:11.930
[Friends] [Emotional problems]

10:09.230 --> 10:10.580
and the case

10:10.630 --> 10:12.070
became a burden on my heart.

10:14.780 --> 10:16.150
As a former police officer,

10:16.340 --> 10:17.150
I really don't want

10:17.790 --> 10:19.230
to have any regrets.

10:19.270 --> 10:19.900
You understand?

10:21.890 --> 10:23.060
Since you're here to

10:23.110 --> 10:24.550
ask about Deng Man's case,

10:25.870 --> 10:27.500
you must want to look into it.

10:27.890 --> 10:28.480
How about this?

10:29.490 --> 10:31.450
No matter what the result is,

10:32.440 --> 10:33.960
you must tell me.

10:35.110 --> 10:35.730
Don't worry.

10:35.790 --> 10:36.910
I'll do my best.

10:38.110 --> 10:38.730
Okay.

10:44.910 --> 10:45.730
Who's it?

10:45.990 --> 10:46.680
Zhong.

10:46.750 --> 10:47.420
It's me.

10:49.960 --> 10:51.560
What a surprise. You miss me?

10:51.740 --> 10:52.410
I need to ask you something.

10:52.670 --> 10:53.190
This is my colleague.

10:53.250 --> 10:54.050
Nice to meet you.

10:55.150 --> 10:55.780
Where is Tang Jie?

10:55.960 --> 10:56.390
In the bedroom.

10:56.430 --> 10:57.690
Honey, Jiang is here.

10:59.630 --> 11:00.310
Tang Jie.

11:00.630 --> 11:01.750
-Come here. I have something to ask you.
-Captain Jiang.

11:01.840 --> 11:02.350
Okay.

11:02.370 --> 11:03.340
Something to drink?

11:03.360 --> 11:04.490
Whatever you have.

11:06.760 --> 11:08.450
What happened? What's the rush?

11:08.830 --> 11:09.450
Hello.

11:09.510 --> 11:10.100
Hello.

11:10.510 --> 11:11.150
It's about Deng Man.

11:13.830 --> 11:14.750
Well,

11:15.150 --> 11:16.430
do you know why she committed suicide

11:16.430 --> 11:17.230
back then?

11:17.940 --> 11:18.740
No.

11:20.030 --> 11:21.280
I just remember

11:21.310 --> 11:23.150
she went out with Lu Yan,

11:23.190 --> 11:24.670
and Lu Yan came back alone.

11:25.070 --> 11:26.910
Did you ask Lu Yan

11:26.930 --> 11:28.330
why she came back alone?

11:29.460 --> 11:30.440
No.

11:31.510 --> 11:33.170
Did you read her suicide note?

11:33.270 --> 11:34.590
No.

11:34.710 --> 11:35.800
When it happened, both Lu Yan and I

11:35.830 --> 11:37.190
took extended leave to go home.

11:37.270 --> 11:38.430
When we came back,

11:38.470 --> 11:39.390
all of Man's stuff

11:39.430 --> 11:40.740
had been taken away

11:40.770 --> 11:41.740
from our dorm.

11:42.760 --> 11:44.060
Was she dating someone

11:44.270 --> 11:45.240
in college?

11:45.270 --> 11:46.310
Did she have a boyfriend?

11:47.350 --> 11:47.880
No way.

11:47.910 --> 11:49.390
She never mentioned it.

11:49.670 --> 11:50.680
She…

11:50.780 --> 11:51.620
You know,

11:51.670 --> 11:52.990
she was quite a loner.

11:53.190 --> 11:54.370
No online dating

11:54.400 --> 11:55.020
either?

11:55.110 --> 11:56.180
No one she was interested in?

11:56.310 --> 11:57.950
Online dating?

11:58.430 --> 11:59.780
I don't think so.

12:00.260 --> 12:01.910
She was always on a scholarship,

12:01.950 --> 12:03.270
living very frugally.

12:03.390 --> 12:04.350
It wasn't until sophomore year

12:04.350 --> 12:06.190
that she saved up enough to buy a smartphone.

12:06.740 --> 12:07.830
Besides me and Lu Yan,

12:07.870 --> 12:09.220
she didn't really have any other friends.

12:13.710 --> 12:14.580
Finished asking her?

12:15.270 --> 12:16.020
Is it my turn?

12:16.270 --> 12:17.400
Why would they ask you?

12:17.430 --> 12:18.610
You were not even close with Man.

12:18.680 --> 12:20.520
Honey, who are you looking down on?

12:20.590 --> 12:21.410
Back in college,

12:21.480 --> 12:22.810
a guy from the dorm next door

12:22.960 --> 12:23.850
liked Deng Man.

12:23.890 --> 12:24.690
Did you two know that?

12:25.430 --> 12:25.960
Who?

12:26.150 --> 12:27.430
The guy next door,

12:27.450 --> 12:28.470
studying engineering.

12:28.790 --> 12:30.540
Later became a director.

12:30.720 --> 12:31.480
Named Wu Qiang.

12:32.870 --> 12:33.560
Well,

12:33.670 --> 12:35.290
he… he knew we were dating

12:35.470 --> 12:37.080
and insisted I help him

12:37.270 --> 12:38.540
ask Deng Man for her number.

12:38.790 --> 12:39.690
I actually went

12:40.030 --> 12:40.890
and asked her,

12:40.990 --> 12:41.950
but Deng Man refused.

12:42.220 --> 12:43.960
Why didn't you mention this before?

12:44.190 --> 12:45.160
I did.

12:45.230 --> 12:46.720
You said all my friends were bad influences

12:46.750 --> 12:47.230
and called him

12:47.230 --> 12:48.580
a toad lusting after a swan.

12:49.000 --> 12:50.210
Are you still in touch with this person?

12:50.390 --> 12:51.330
Yes.

12:51.870 --> 12:53.120
I even reached out to him a while ago

12:53.150 --> 12:54.280
to help me direct a play.

12:55.030 --> 12:55.870
But for sure, her death

12:55.870 --> 12:56.940
had nothing to do with him.

12:57.470 --> 12:59.160
When Deng Man died,

12:59.210 --> 13:00.870
he was studying abroad on an exchange program.

13:01.270 --> 13:02.350
He came back later

13:02.510 --> 13:03.610
and got a girlfriend.

13:03.820 --> 13:05.310
He probably forgot about Deng Man a long time ago.

13:05.550 --> 13:07.190
Then why are you saying these things?

13:07.920 --> 13:10.080
I haven't mentioned the key point yet.

13:12.570 --> 13:13.840
I went to ask for her number

13:13.870 --> 13:15.010
for him, right?

13:15.110 --> 13:16.510
I went to the library to find Deng Man.

13:16.670 --> 13:18.220
At the time, it seemed like

13:18.990 --> 13:20.150
she was waiting for someone.

13:41.510 --> 13:42.910
I knew you'd come.

13:44.690 --> 13:45.270
Hey,

13:45.410 --> 13:46.170
it's me,

13:46.470 --> 13:47.860
Tang Jie's boyfriend, Zhong.

13:48.040 --> 13:48.750
You remember, right?

13:50.890 --> 13:52.310
One of my buddies likes you.

13:52.470 --> 13:53.680
Can I get your contact info?

13:53.770 --> 13:54.440
Sorry,

13:54.470 --> 13:55.840
I'm not looking to make friends.

13:55.990 --> 13:56.820
I'll get going.

13:58.100 --> 13:58.810
Wait, you…

13:59.600 --> 14:01.220
It might not be someone she liked.

14:01.470 --> 14:02.690
Maybe she was waiting for a friend.

14:09.110 --> 14:09.760
Wait.

14:10.060 --> 14:10.880
Back then, wasn't she

14:10.910 --> 14:11.830
pretty close to you?

14:11.830 --> 14:13.400
She always went to watch you play basketball.

14:13.590 --> 14:14.320
Nonsense.

14:14.340 --> 14:15.340
She wasn't there for me.

14:15.910 --> 14:16.670
Then who was she there for?

14:39.790 --> 14:41.840
Deng Man comes every day.

14:42.470 --> 14:43.380
Who is she here for?

14:45.300 --> 14:46.010
Me.

14:46.040 --> 14:46.920
Shut up.

14:46.940 --> 14:48.910
Get over yourself.

14:49.680 --> 14:51.160
I think she's here for Jiang.

14:51.520 --> 14:52.340
Shut up.

14:52.390 --> 14:53.390
She's a good friend of Lu Yan.

14:53.410 --> 14:54.300
Don't talk nonsense.

14:57.070 --> 14:59.110
Who was she there for?

15:02.820 --> 15:03.350
Wait.

15:03.350 --> 15:04.080
Aren't you curious

15:04.120 --> 15:05.550
who she was waiting for in the library?

15:16.930 --> 15:24.840
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

15:17.000 --> 15:17.600
Come on, guys.

15:17.630 --> 15:18.670
Here's the information we've got.

15:19.250 --> 15:21.240
Captain Jiang and I just met

15:21.270 --> 15:22.670
the police officer in charge of Deng Man's case back then

15:22.750 --> 15:23.710
to learn more about her death.

15:24.430 --> 15:26.150
He said that after Deng Man died,

15:26.190 --> 15:28.170
someone sent an anonymous letter to the police station,

15:28.630 --> 15:29.930
requesting to reopen the case.

15:30.640 --> 15:32.000
Although we can't

15:32.030 --> 15:33.200
link Wang Qianqian's case

15:33.220 --> 15:35.030
to Deng Man's case now,

15:35.230 --> 15:36.230
we can

15:36.270 --> 15:38.000
first go over

15:38.030 --> 15:38.950
Deng Man's case

15:39.150 --> 15:40.270
to see if we can find

15:40.310 --> 15:41.230
any useful clues.

15:42.070 --> 15:42.730
Liu Hao.

15:43.150 --> 15:44.930
Have you got Deng Man's

15:45.110 --> 15:45.880
suicide note?

15:46.070 --> 15:47.130
I'll put it on screen.

15:50.350 --> 15:51.150
Back then,

15:51.190 --> 15:52.600
they had a handwriting analysis done

15:52.620 --> 15:53.670
and confirmed that Deng Man wrote it.

15:57.380 --> 15:59.910
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

15:57.550 --> 15:58.400
It's as if God

15:58.430 --> 15:59.750
enjoys tormenting me.

16:00.550 --> 16:01.630
I'm average-looking,

16:01.660 --> 16:03.670
an average student from an ordinary family.

16:04.270 --> 16:05.200
So

16:05.640 --> 16:06.720
I'm destined to not get

16:06.750 --> 16:08.030
the life I want?

16:08.770 --> 16:11.230
I really want to say I don't hate you.

16:11.470 --> 16:12.710
But at the end of my life,

16:12.710 --> 16:14.070
I don't want to lie to you anymore.

16:14.580 --> 16:15.360
Yes.

16:15.910 --> 16:17.070
I hate you.

16:17.730 --> 16:20.140
You took away my only light.

16:20.470 --> 16:21.510
I curse you.

16:21.550 --> 16:23.540
May you never find happiness.

16:23.830 --> 16:26.350
May your life be filled, every moment,

16:26.430 --> 16:29.110
with suspicion, betrayal, and pain,

16:29.200 --> 16:31.010
until it ends in ruin!

16:31.150 --> 16:31.960
Jiang.

16:32.110 --> 16:34.370
Could the "you" mentioned here

16:35.150 --> 16:36.490
be someone she liked?

16:38.300 --> 16:39.620
That's not for sure.

16:43.630 --> 16:44.270
On the anonymous letter,

16:44.310 --> 16:45.610
there were no fingerprints and no address.

16:45.940 --> 16:47.350
No more information for now.

16:46.060 --> 16:49.810
[Deng Man didn't commit suicide. She was murdered. Please restart the investigation.]

16:51.340 --> 16:52.030
Okay.

16:54.080 --> 16:54.860
Yiming.

16:54.880 --> 16:56.220
Do you have any leads over there?

16:54.950 --> 16:58.230
[Deng Man didn't commit suicide. She was murdered. Please restart the investigation.]

16:56.350 --> 16:57.790
The trash can containing Wang Qianqian

16:57.790 --> 16:58.370
has been found.

16:58.430 --> 16:59.630
But when it was discovered,

16:59.670 --> 17:00.870
it had been burnt.

17:00.870 --> 17:02.170
Only some remnants were left.

17:02.670 --> 17:03.350
Okay.

17:03.540 --> 17:05.430
Contact the technical department

17:05.670 --> 17:07.270
to see if there is

17:07.470 --> 17:08.560
any crucial evidence on the remnants.

17:08.579 --> 17:09.150
Okay.

17:12.990 --> 17:14.060
Recently,

17:14.589 --> 17:15.690
the workload has been heavy.

17:16.190 --> 17:17.210
You've been working hard.

17:17.740 --> 17:18.670
If there is anything,

17:19.270 --> 17:20.020
report it immediately,

17:20.609 --> 17:21.050
okay?

17:22.150 --> 17:22.930
Everyone, back to work.

17:25.609 --> 17:26.510
By the way, Captain Jiang,

17:26.819 --> 17:28.079
Dr. Lu came by today.

17:29.560 --> 17:30.370
For what?

17:30.790 --> 17:32.090
She learned that

17:32.110 --> 17:33.260
Deng Man and Wang Qianqian

17:33.300 --> 17:34.610
died at the same place.

17:34.720 --> 17:35.270
She came over

17:35.270 --> 17:36.090
to provide us with clues.

17:36.510 --> 17:37.540
We asked her

17:37.710 --> 17:38.560
if Deng Man had

17:38.590 --> 17:39.540
other social relationships.

17:39.750 --> 17:40.640
She said she didn't know either.

17:44.820 --> 17:46.350
How was she?

17:46.500 --> 17:47.420
Not bad.

17:47.450 --> 17:48.600
We were really worried about her.

17:48.790 --> 17:49.390
She said

17:49.420 --> 17:50.100
she can handle it

17:50.250 --> 17:51.130
and wants to know

17:51.190 --> 17:52.270
who the murderer is.

17:54.280 --> 17:55.010
I see.

18:06.710 --> 18:07.150
Come in.

18:08.830 --> 18:09.680
Director Xing,

18:11.290 --> 18:11.760
um,

18:11.790 --> 18:14.030
I'd like to go to Ninghai University Library

18:14.070 --> 18:15.140
to check some of their

18:15.390 --> 18:17.020
previous borrowing records.

18:17.830 --> 18:18.600
Could you

18:18.750 --> 18:20.320
help me inform them?

18:20.830 --> 18:21.850
No problem.

18:22.030 --> 18:23.130
I'll make the arrangements.

18:23.370 --> 18:24.450
I'll head over now.

18:25.430 --> 18:25.950
I'm leaving then.

18:25.990 --> 18:26.900
Alright, go ahead.

18:35.200 --> 18:35.940
Thank you.

18:42.120 --> 18:43.190
Man didn't seem to have joined

18:43.190 --> 18:44.250
any campus organizations.

18:45.370 --> 18:46.360
Where should I start looking?

18:47.480 --> 18:48.370
Wen Peng,

18:47.550 --> 18:55.820
[Sharing New Ideas, Spreading Inspiration Along the Way]
[Welcome Outstanding Alumni Back to Campus for an Exchange]

18:48.560 --> 18:49.690
thank you for coming back

18:49.810 --> 18:51.160
to give this talk today.

18:51.480 --> 18:52.470
After the session,

18:52.590 --> 18:53.630
you must spend more time

18:53.740 --> 18:54.400
interacting with the students.

18:54.790 --> 18:55.490
What do you think?

18:55.520 --> 18:56.150
Do you have time?

18:55.910 --> 19:00.440
[Alumni Exchange Meeting]

18:56.590 --> 18:57.030
Yes,

18:57.190 --> 18:57.910
of course, I have time.

18:58.920 --> 18:59.720
It's been so many years

18:59.750 --> 19:00.510
since I came back.

19:00.560 --> 19:02.540
This time, it's all thanks to you.

19:03.230 --> 19:04.600
Back then, you were

19:04.630 --> 19:05.720
an outstanding graduate of Medicine.

19:05.750 --> 19:06.750
I truly didn't expect you

19:06.790 --> 19:08.220
to switch fields so drastically

19:08.240 --> 19:09.440
and even go abroad

19:09.470 --> 19:10.780
to study arts management.

19:11.070 --> 19:11.670
After you returned,

19:11.710 --> 19:12.880
you even started a talent agency.

19:13.540 --> 19:14.170
Yeah,

19:14.570 --> 19:15.930
back then, it was you who presented me

19:15.950 --> 19:17.240
with the Outstanding Graduate award.

19:18.350 --> 19:19.160
From your graduating class,

19:19.200 --> 19:19.910
the two people

19:19.910 --> 19:20.880
I remember the most clearly

19:20.910 --> 19:21.670
are you and Jiang Chengyi.

19:22.180 --> 19:23.110
I still recall that back then,

19:23.150 --> 19:24.110
the two of you were

19:24.150 --> 19:24.790
the stars of the school,

19:25.230 --> 19:26.710
sweeping all the major

19:26.750 --> 19:27.590
and minor competitions

19:27.610 --> 19:28.750
to take the top two spots.

19:28.890 --> 19:32.350
[Alumni Exchange Meeting]

19:29.150 --> 19:29.780
Wen Peng,

19:29.980 --> 19:30.950
I gotta go.

19:31.590 --> 19:32.170
Alright.

19:32.510 --> 19:33.750
See you later.

19:33.780 --> 19:34.360
See you later.

19:52.300 --> 19:53.440
Wen Peng.

19:54.340 --> 19:55.000
Wen Peng.

19:55.070 --> 19:55.870
Everything inside is ready.

19:55.910 --> 19:56.650
Let's go in.

19:57.590 --> 19:58.180
Alright.

20:09.870 --> 20:10.390
Miss,

20:10.410 --> 20:11.840
I've told you before,

20:11.950 --> 20:12.830
this involves

20:12.010 --> 20:17.210
[Ninghai University]

20:12.830 --> 20:14.130
the student's privacy.

20:14.240 --> 20:14.910
I can't just

20:14.950 --> 20:15.880
let you see

20:15.950 --> 20:16.790
her personal records.

20:16.820 --> 20:18.360
I really am her good friend.

20:18.510 --> 20:19.790
You can check my records.

20:19.920 --> 20:21.210
I graduated in 2014.

20:21.310 --> 20:22.350
I believe you,

20:22.440 --> 20:24.060
but these are two different things.

20:22.530 --> 20:28.360
[Ninghai University]

20:24.480 --> 20:26.510
Why don't you apply to the principal?

20:26.540 --> 20:27.310
If he agrees,

20:27.340 --> 20:28.030
then I'll let you see them.

20:28.110 --> 20:28.500
Does that work?

20:28.590 --> 20:28.950
Hello.

20:28.950 --> 20:29.430
You…

20:30.240 --> 20:31.600
I'm Jiang Chengyi.

20:31.620 --> 20:32.830
Your principal knows I'm coming

20:32.860 --> 20:33.880
to check the records.

20:34.990 --> 20:35.490
Yes,

20:35.510 --> 20:36.030
Principal Chen

20:36.070 --> 20:37.230
called this morning.

20:37.260 --> 20:38.570
Alright, come in with me.

20:38.610 --> 20:39.220
Okay.

20:43.280 --> 20:45.860
You're here to look up Deng Man's records too?

20:49.090 --> 20:50.080
Come with me.

20:50.530 --> 20:51.890
You were her best friend.

20:52.030 --> 20:52.800
I need your help.

20:58.080 --> 20:58.750
Thank you.

21:00.100 --> 21:02.140
[Ninghai University]

21:05.580 --> 21:06.100
[Name: Deng Man]

21:06.100 --> 21:09.350
[Address: Unit 305, Huaxi Complex, Yaojia Town, Changping County, Ningxi]

21:22.500 --> 21:23.720
Other than

21:24.030 --> 21:25.960
the contacts listed in the records,

21:26.030 --> 21:27.710
do you know if Deng Man had

21:27.790 --> 21:28.710
any other relatives

21:28.750 --> 21:29.750
or close friends?

21:32.440 --> 21:33.920
They're all I know about.

21:39.190 --> 21:40.350
Earlier,

21:40.470 --> 21:41.350
I talked with the officer

21:41.350 --> 21:43.270
who handled Deng Man's case

21:43.390 --> 21:44.380
back then.

21:46.230 --> 21:46.830
He said

21:46.830 --> 21:48.120
the police received

21:48.390 --> 21:49.310
an anonymous letter

21:49.350 --> 21:51.000
in 2019.

21:52.790 --> 21:53.480
An...

21:53.750 --> 21:54.750
anonymous letter?

21:58.040 --> 21:59.330
So who do you think

22:00.950 --> 22:03.320
around Deng Man might have sent

22:03.350 --> 22:04.790
an anonymous letter like that?

22:05.910 --> 22:06.460
I…

22:08.410 --> 22:09.460
I don't know.

22:16.410 --> 22:20.280
[Deng Man] [Kinesiology] [Physiology] [Medical Physics]

22:20.150 --> 22:21.940
Hiroshima Mon Amour…

22:23.010 --> 22:24.520
Do you remember this book?

22:25.350 --> 22:27.270
Hiroshima Mon Amour?

22:28.190 --> 22:28.870
No.

22:31.510 --> 22:34.020
From March

22:34.110 --> 22:35.550
to October 2015,

22:36.460 --> 22:38.810
Deng Man borrowed this book

22:36.840 --> 22:40.120
[Deng Man] [Hiroshima Mon Amour]

22:38.830 --> 22:40.030
six times in a row.

22:41.650 --> 22:44.600
She kept it for a few days each time.

22:44.150 --> 22:47.930
[Deng Man] [Hiroshima Mon Amour] [Not Returned]

22:45.540 --> 22:47.420
The last time was October 19,

22:48.910 --> 22:49.810
and she never returned it.

22:50.600 --> 22:51.550
Did this book have

22:51.590 --> 22:52.790
any special meaning to her?

22:53.790 --> 22:55.230
I really don't remember. I...

22:56.710 --> 22:57.640
I just remember we

22:57.670 --> 22:59.040
were so busy back then.

22:59.500 --> 23:01.470
We didn't have time for extracurricular reading.

23:02.330 --> 23:03.310
Then where

23:03.350 --> 23:04.550
did she take that book?

23:22.800 --> 23:24.830
If Man liked that book so much,

23:26.180 --> 23:28.030
why didn't I hear her mention it?

23:29.970 --> 23:31.600
She borrowed it so many times in a year.

23:31.920 --> 23:34.600
She either really loved that book,

23:34.620 --> 23:36.030
or it had some

23:36.710 --> 23:37.820
other significance

23:37.980 --> 23:39.170
or purpose.

23:40.110 --> 23:41.330
What purpose?

23:42.520 --> 23:43.310
For example, it might contain

23:43.310 --> 23:44.350
important information,

23:44.390 --> 23:45.320
or

23:45.670 --> 23:46.550
she could've used it

23:46.590 --> 23:47.740
to pass messages.

23:54.920 --> 23:55.560
Lu Yan,

23:56.810 --> 23:59.070
there's something I want to tell you.

24:00.960 --> 24:03.140
Wang Qianqian's death has nothing to do with you.

24:04.590 --> 24:05.160
Then…

24:07.300 --> 24:09.250
Then has the killer been caught?

24:09.910 --> 24:10.760
Deng Man

24:11.320 --> 24:12.590
and Wang Qianqian

24:13.230 --> 24:14.550
were both your good friends,

24:16.190 --> 24:17.000
and they both died

24:17.030 --> 24:18.570
in the same lake.

24:19.490 --> 24:21.300
I think it's too much of a coincidence.

24:24.810 --> 24:26.230
Lately, when you're alone,

24:26.750 --> 24:27.590
you must be careful

24:28.180 --> 24:29.020
and stay safe.

24:32.320 --> 24:33.390
I understand.

24:37.070 --> 24:38.780
I know you don't want to face me,

24:40.040 --> 24:41.470
but I really wish

24:41.500 --> 24:43.110
you could move on.

24:43.440 --> 24:44.600
Pull yourself together

24:45.590 --> 24:46.390
and get out of the bad mood

24:46.430 --> 24:47.230
as soon as you can,

24:47.740 --> 24:48.290
okay?

24:50.960 --> 24:51.990
As for the case,

24:52.390 --> 24:53.300
leave it to me.

24:53.780 --> 24:54.740
Don't worry about it.

25:11.880 --> 25:12.570
What's it?

25:13.190 --> 25:13.840
Jiang.

25:13.990 --> 25:14.830
We found the guy who sold the killer

25:14.830 --> 25:15.810
the anesthetic.

25:17.980 --> 25:18.800
I see.

25:26.390 --> 25:27.460
Take good care of yourself.

25:29.140 --> 25:30.020
I'll be going now.

25:46.280 --> 25:48.770
[Anshan, Ninghai Public Security
Criminal Investigation Unit]

25:50.350 --> 25:51.390
What exactly happened that day?

25:51.420 --> 25:52.340
Tell us again.

25:54.500 --> 25:56.510
It was past midnight.

25:56.630 --> 25:57.680
I was already asleep,

25:57.750 --> 25:58.800
and then someone came in,

25:58.880 --> 26:00.150
saying she wanted sevoflurane.

26:01.350 --> 26:02.970
A stranger wanted to buy it, and you just sold it?

26:03.150 --> 26:04.130
Weren't you afraid she'd report you?

26:04.190 --> 26:05.810
I was worried,

26:06.070 --> 26:06.860
but she

26:06.960 --> 26:07.820
threw down 20,000 yuan

26:07.870 --> 26:08.830
right there.

26:08.920 --> 26:09.420
I...

26:10.250 --> 26:10.750
I just...

26:10.750 --> 26:11.470
Your drug caused someone's death.

26:11.470 --> 26:12.070
Do you know that?

26:12.550 --> 26:13.700
I'm innocent, officer!

26:13.870 --> 26:15.030
I didn't kill anyone!

26:15.050 --> 26:16.630
-Calm down!
-I'm just a seller. I...

26:18.510 --> 26:19.680
No one said you killed anyone.

26:26.540 --> 26:27.350
That night,

26:27.970 --> 26:29.090
did she come with any other people?

26:29.590 --> 26:30.260
She came alone.

26:31.070 --> 26:31.840
Other than her appearance,

26:31.870 --> 26:33.120
are there any other

26:33.400 --> 26:35.500
distinctive features you can describe?

26:38.460 --> 26:38.990
Well,

26:39.240 --> 26:41.320
some other people had come to me before

26:41.340 --> 26:42.700
to buy GHB.

26:42.800 --> 26:44.000
But she came in

26:44.030 --> 26:44.920
and directly asked for sevoflurane.

26:44.950 --> 26:46.280
I was stunned.

26:46.420 --> 26:47.960
I didn't react right away.

26:48.670 --> 26:49.670
Show it to him.

26:53.800 --> 26:54.530
Take a close look.

26:57.830 --> 26:58.770
No.

27:00.340 --> 27:01.690
I think it might be her.

27:02.520 --> 27:05.010
I just remember her big eyes.

27:06.740 --> 27:08.480
Her hair looked very similar to this.

27:08.870 --> 27:10.030
She was about…

27:10.660 --> 27:11.830
160 cm tall, I guess.

27:12.710 --> 27:13.520
Anyway, no other woman

27:13.550 --> 27:14.750
had bought that from me before.

27:14.960 --> 27:16.060
I remember it very clearly.

27:19.770 --> 27:21.350
Alright, get the sketch artist

27:21.400 --> 27:22.150
to draw that woman

27:22.190 --> 27:23.110
based on his description.

27:23.460 --> 27:23.950
Okay.

27:25.260 --> 27:26.690
[Reception Room]

27:29.000 --> 27:29.900
Captain Jiang.

27:29.720 --> 27:32.050
[Serve the Public as Police; Enforce the Law for the People]

27:30.710 --> 27:31.300
Qin Yue.

27:31.530 --> 27:32.030
Jiang.

27:32.090 --> 27:32.420
Captain Jiang.

27:32.470 --> 27:32.920
How's it going?

27:32.960 --> 27:34.540
I'm about to run a comparison.

27:34.570 --> 27:35.860
This is a sketch based on

27:35.860 --> 27:36.790
the seller's statement.

27:36.810 --> 27:37.590
It's a young woman,

27:37.590 --> 27:38.350
about 160 cm tall,

27:38.390 --> 27:39.240
very thin.

27:40.650 --> 27:41.710
She's familiar with anesthetics

27:41.710 --> 27:42.890
and likely has a medical background.

27:43.950 --> 27:44.750
Hurry up with the comparison.

27:44.770 --> 27:46.330
Since there's a breakthrough in this case,

27:46.420 --> 27:47.960
focus all efforts on this lead

27:48.230 --> 27:49.030
and dig deeper.

27:49.270 --> 27:49.710
Got it.

27:49.740 --> 27:50.710
Alright, I'm on it.

27:50.870 --> 27:51.330
Let's go.

28:02.210 --> 28:04.170
The leg stretch is taking way too long.

28:04.710 --> 28:06.110
Coach Zhou wants everyone

28:06.180 --> 28:07.340
to fully stretch.

28:07.900 --> 28:09.160
Coach Zhou has been

28:09.190 --> 28:10.510
working here as a PE coach for over ten years.

28:10.590 --> 28:11.730
Just do as he says.

28:21.230 --> 28:23.430
Back then, Man chose volleyball as her elective.

28:23.490 --> 28:25.850
Could she have made other friends

28:25.870 --> 28:27.290
in volleyball class?

28:29.090 --> 28:29.590
Alright,

28:29.710 --> 28:30.820
that's it for today.

28:30.850 --> 28:32.020
Well done. Class dismissed.

28:32.790 --> 28:33.800
Let's go.

28:38.870 --> 28:39.740
Coach Zhou.

28:41.940 --> 28:43.220
You're Lu Yan, right?

28:43.520 --> 28:44.840
You still remember me?

28:45.570 --> 28:47.160
You were on the cheerleading team.

28:47.300 --> 28:48.190
I vaguely remember.

28:49.030 --> 28:50.400
Can I ask you something?

28:50.430 --> 28:50.830
Are you

28:51.100 --> 28:52.420
free right now?

28:53.060 --> 28:54.900
My wife's at home alone,

28:54.950 --> 28:55.850
and she needs care.

28:55.960 --> 28:57.190
The caregiver's about to leave.

28:57.290 --> 28:58.720
It won't take long.

29:01.410 --> 29:02.990
If you don't mind,

29:03.010 --> 29:04.070
come with me.

29:06.650 --> 29:07.740
[Certificate of Honor]

29:31.150 --> 29:32.420
Here, freshly made chicken soup.

29:35.260 --> 29:36.130
Have a sip.

29:45.450 --> 29:47.350
It's still a bit hot.

29:47.740 --> 29:48.990
Let it cool for a bit.

29:52.310 --> 29:53.580
A student is here.

29:53.710 --> 29:54.900
I'll chat with her for a bit.

29:55.920 --> 29:57.930
If anything comes up, ring the bell for me.

30:08.510 --> 30:09.200
Sorry

30:09.570 --> 30:10.400
to keep you waiting.

30:13.800 --> 30:14.720
Coach Zhou,

30:14.770 --> 30:15.640
it's okay.

30:16.130 --> 30:17.390
As a medical student, I know very well

30:17.480 --> 30:18.790
how hard it is to look after someone

30:18.810 --> 30:19.510
for so long.

30:20.650 --> 30:21.770
At the end of the day,

30:22.710 --> 30:23.950
it's all because of me.

30:25.120 --> 30:26.350
15 years ago,

30:26.380 --> 30:28.260
if she hadn't gone out

30:28.310 --> 30:29.630
to buy fever medicine for me,

30:30.290 --> 30:32.080
she wouldn't have gotten into that accident

30:32.550 --> 30:33.950
and become bedridden

30:33.950 --> 30:35.070
and unable to speak.

30:35.540 --> 30:36.830
I owe her this.

30:39.020 --> 30:40.110
Enough about me.

30:40.650 --> 30:41.660
What do you want to ask?

30:44.180 --> 30:46.350
Coach Zhou, do you still remember

30:46.590 --> 30:47.590
Deng Man?

30:49.600 --> 30:50.270
I do.

30:53.350 --> 30:54.960
A pretty introverted girl.

30:55.510 --> 30:57.090
She was in Medicine like you, right?

30:57.470 --> 30:57.960
Yes.

30:57.990 --> 30:59.350
D-Do you remember if she signed up

30:59.390 --> 31:00.630
for your volleyball class?

31:02.990 --> 31:03.840
The police came

31:03.870 --> 31:05.220
to ask me about her.

31:05.870 --> 31:06.800
I remember.

31:08.710 --> 31:09.580
Then,

31:10.030 --> 31:11.970
do you recall

31:12.310 --> 31:13.920
if she had anyone

31:14.000 --> 31:14.910
in class

31:14.950 --> 31:15.680
she was particularly close to

31:15.710 --> 31:17.390
or good friends with?

31:18.670 --> 31:19.590
I don't know about that.

31:24.410 --> 31:26.080
I only know she had a crush on someone.

31:30.200 --> 31:31.020
A crush?

31:34.830 --> 31:36.080
At first,

31:37.450 --> 31:38.880
she often came to the basketball court

31:38.900 --> 31:39.950
to watch us train.

31:41.760 --> 31:43.510
But you know those boys,

31:43.550 --> 31:45.200
they couldn't focus when there was a girl

31:45.270 --> 31:46.490
sitting on the sidelines.

31:46.950 --> 31:48.340
One time, I talked with her,

31:49.650 --> 31:50.590
telling her not to interfere

31:50.630 --> 31:51.380
with our training.

31:56.060 --> 31:56.940
Deng Man,

31:57.110 --> 31:57.830
you keep coming here,

31:57.850 --> 31:59.110
and it's affecting our training.

32:00.480 --> 32:02.070
Please don't come again.

32:08.050 --> 32:08.790
Later,

32:08.820 --> 32:10.350
I ran into her on campus.

32:11.460 --> 32:13.170
She seemed to be in a bad mood.

32:14.850 --> 32:16.840
I was just about to comfort her

32:18.420 --> 32:19.870
when I saw Jiang Chengyi coming over.

32:26.550 --> 32:27.500
Jiang Chengyi.

32:26.790 --> 32:30.870
[Ninghai University]

32:29.710 --> 32:30.670
What are you doing here?

32:32.720 --> 32:34.030
I need to talk to you.

32:35.070 --> 32:35.860
Go ahead.

32:39.060 --> 32:40.860
Alright, if you need anything,

32:40.910 --> 32:42.100
just let me know.

32:42.130 --> 32:42.670
I'm leaving.

33:14.370 --> 33:16.420
I didn't hear clearly

33:16.740 --> 33:17.930
what they talked about.

33:19.230 --> 33:20.740
Jiang Chengyi left soon.

33:22.110 --> 33:22.830
Deng Man stayed there alone

33:22.850 --> 33:24.000
and cried for a long time.

33:32.080 --> 33:33.730
I think maybe…

33:35.830 --> 33:36.960
she confessed to Jiang Chengyi

33:36.990 --> 33:37.990
and got rejected.

33:39.740 --> 33:40.240
Of course,

33:40.270 --> 33:41.590
this is just my guess.

33:41.680 --> 33:43.000
No real basis.

33:46.570 --> 33:48.020
It's all in the past.

34:02.110 --> 34:03.270
Give me a minute.

34:03.310 --> 34:04.400
It's okay, Coach Zhou.

34:04.640 --> 34:05.630
I should get going.

34:06.010 --> 34:07.010
I'll be off now.

34:07.300 --> 34:08.330
Thanks for talking with me.

34:09.030 --> 34:10.440
Take care. You can see yourself out.

34:34.350 --> 34:34.790
Here.

34:35.880 --> 34:37.230
It's cooled down enough.

34:41.699 --> 34:42.150
Here.

35:18.750 --> 35:19.750
I've already

35:20.350 --> 35:21.690
done what you said.

35:40.000 --> 35:40.910
Have you made it home?

35:47.440 --> 35:48.040
Wen Peng.

35:48.540 --> 35:49.110
Lu Yan,

35:49.410 --> 35:50.230
what are you doing here?

35:51.390 --> 35:53.880
I don't have much going on today,

35:53.900 --> 35:55.080
so I came back to campus for a walk.

35:55.400 --> 35:56.340
What about you?

35:57.050 --> 35:58.600
Principal Chen asked me to give a lecture.

35:58.630 --> 35:59.430
It just ended.

35:59.480 --> 36:01.170
I was thinking of visiting Coach Zhou,

36:01.240 --> 36:03.220
but he said he's taking care of his wife

36:03.240 --> 36:04.440
and suggested leaving it for another day.

36:08.540 --> 36:09.380
What's wrong?

36:09.640 --> 36:10.720
You're in a bad mood?

36:11.940 --> 36:12.700
No.

36:14.720 --> 36:16.460
Then how about we grab a meal together?

36:18.610 --> 36:19.350
I'm good.

36:19.370 --> 36:20.160
I'm not feeling

36:20.190 --> 36:21.150
very hungry.

36:24.640 --> 36:25.830
Let me give you a ride back, then.

36:28.810 --> 36:30.090
My car's over there.

36:30.110 --> 36:31.360
It's hard to find a taxi now.

36:31.400 --> 36:32.560
It's on my way anyway.

36:34.950 --> 36:35.580
Thanks.

36:44.230 --> 36:45.870
Actually, these past few days,

36:45.900 --> 36:46.820
I've been hesitating

36:47.370 --> 36:49.190
whether to visit you or not.

36:51.810 --> 36:53.190
I called you a few times,

36:53.230 --> 36:54.100
but you didn't answer.

36:55.040 --> 36:55.810
I know…

36:57.170 --> 36:58.110
you're still upset

36:58.130 --> 36:59.990
about Qianqian.

37:03.110 --> 37:04.280
I've been in touch with

37:04.470 --> 37:05.280
Dr. Han,

37:05.390 --> 37:07.230
Tang Jie, and Zhong,

37:07.500 --> 37:09.110
getting updates

37:09.150 --> 37:10.110
on how you're doing.

37:10.600 --> 37:12.130
I think staying with them

37:12.150 --> 37:12.670
would…

37:13.750 --> 37:14.790
would be better for you.

37:17.830 --> 37:18.780
I'm home.

37:18.800 --> 37:19.870
I'll head in.

37:22.940 --> 37:23.460
Lu Yan.

37:30.610 --> 37:31.450
Do you know

37:31.470 --> 37:32.550
what kind of impression

37:32.580 --> 37:34.070
you left on me during college?

37:38.230 --> 37:40.130
What was it called again?

37:42.180 --> 37:43.000
A...

37:43.720 --> 37:44.730
rookie studyholic.

37:46.920 --> 37:49.750
Roo... rookie studyholic?

37:51.130 --> 37:53.320
Although in many ways she was pretty average,

37:53.390 --> 37:55.250
she was always very hardworking,

37:55.270 --> 37:55.880
very brave,

37:56.490 --> 37:57.690
and kept pushing herself.

38:01.130 --> 38:02.480
I don't think

38:02.820 --> 38:04.160
fate can defeat

38:04.190 --> 38:05.210
a rookie studyholic.

38:05.520 --> 38:06.760
I believe you can

38:07.570 --> 38:09.520
let go of the past

38:10.240 --> 38:11.330
and start fresh.

38:12.890 --> 38:13.870
I know,

38:14.240 --> 38:15.370
but I think

38:16.240 --> 38:17.620
it'll take time.

38:18.020 --> 38:19.160
Because that night,

38:19.190 --> 38:20.490
Qianqian kept calling me,

38:20.550 --> 38:21.750
but I didn't pick up. I...

38:22.400 --> 38:23.700
I feel so guilty about it.

38:23.930 --> 38:24.780
You don't understand.

38:25.030 --> 38:25.790
I do.

38:26.760 --> 38:27.970
Really, I really do.

38:28.170 --> 38:29.030
Because that night,

38:29.050 --> 38:30.330
she called me too.

38:31.260 --> 38:32.490
She apologized to me,

38:32.570 --> 38:33.470
saying sorry

38:33.490 --> 38:34.820
for not attending my premiere.

38:37.200 --> 38:38.910
I've been thinking these past few days,

38:39.310 --> 38:40.670
that if I had

38:40.820 --> 38:41.800
given her more tickets that day,

38:41.870 --> 38:42.570
or…

38:43.220 --> 38:44.160
talked to her longer

38:44.230 --> 38:44.990
when she called,

38:44.990 --> 38:45.740
maybe it would...

38:46.090 --> 38:47.070
maybe this wouldn't

38:47.090 --> 38:47.800
have happened.

38:49.000 --> 38:50.460
I feel just like you. I...

38:51.040 --> 38:52.940
I feel so guilty, so full of regret.

38:57.060 --> 38:57.940
You're right.

38:58.610 --> 38:59.640
Someone who hasn't experienced

38:59.710 --> 39:01.050
something like this

39:01.150 --> 39:02.360
wouldn't understand.

39:09.720 --> 39:11.030
So I understand you.

39:19.570 --> 39:20.300
Lu Yan.

39:24.220 --> 39:26.550
What happened can change us,

39:27.210 --> 39:28.670
but we can't change what happened.

39:29.970 --> 39:32.300
Let the past stay in the past.

39:33.880 --> 39:35.230
If you're feeling upset

39:35.710 --> 39:36.840
or need help,

39:36.870 --> 39:38.020
come to me.

39:41.010 --> 39:41.930
I'm always here.

39:44.740 --> 39:45.580
Okay.

39:47.220 --> 39:48.440
I'll head back now.
